== 迴響 ==
上映後，獲得了極高的票房和良好的評價。

=== 專業評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度82%，基於168條評論，平均分為6.9/10，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到74分，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得7.8分，評價良好。

==女性版電影==
2015年10月，{{link-en|傑瑞·溫特勞布|Jerry Weintraub}}、史蒂芬·索德柏和喬治·克隆尼提出了新《瞞天過海》的構思，就是以[[珊卓·布拉克|珊卓·布拉克]]為主的女性版本《瞞天過海》。奧利維亞·米爾希與[[蓋瑞·羅斯|蓋瑞·羅斯]]分別簽約擔任編劇和導演<ref>{{cite news|title=Exclusive: All-Female ‘Ocean’s Eleven’ In The Works Starring Sandra Bullock, With Gary Ross Directing|work=Indiewire|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/exclusive-all-female-oceans-eleven-in-the-works-starring-sandra-bullock-with-gary-ross-directing-20151029|date=29 October 2015|accessdate=2016-08-17|archive-date=2015-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151111001734/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/exclusive-all-female-oceans-eleven-in-the-works-starring-sandra-bullock-with-gary-ross-directing-20151029|dead-url=no}}</ref>。演員[[凱特·布蘭琪|凱特·布蘭琪]]、[[海倫娜·寶漢·卡特|海倫娜·寶漢·卡特]]、{{link-en|敏迪・卡靈|Mindy Kaling}}、[[安·海瑟薇|安·海瑟薇]]、[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]和[[奧卡菲娜|奧卡菲娜]]確認加入<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/692377-cate-blanchett-in-talks-to-join-all-female-oceans-eleven |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-08-17 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108163436/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/692377-cate-blanchett-in-talks-to-join-all-female-oceans-eleven |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/elizabeth-banks-oceans-eleven/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-08-17 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308140100/https://www.slashfilm.com/elizabeth-banks-oceans-eleven/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/oceans-eight-rihanna-anne-hathaway-sandra-bullock-cate-blanchett-awkwafina-helena-bonham-carter-mindy-kaling-1201801342/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-08-17 |archive-date=2016-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810220902/http://deadline.com/2016/08/oceans-eight-rihanna-anne-hathaway-sandra-bullock-cate-blanchett-awkwafina-helena-bonham-carter-mindy-kaling-1201801342/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影定名為《[[Ocean's_Eight|Ocean's Eight]]》。電影定於2018年6月8日上映。

